{"tid":312990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大英帝國 VS 地獄鬼國軍艦質素","createTime":"2017-07-08T03:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T07:59:53.000Z","uid":4493,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fed2e2cc221b6a54e0ed320a5b456c8f7c1b19e4","tid":312990,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:05:52.000Z","msg":"皇家海軍HMS Belfast<br />\n建於1939年 經歷多場戰役<br />\n包括中雷龍骨受損 炸彈攻擊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/105411_e70cd74f066a8ff06f127ae878fe9d0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F105411_e70cd74f066a8ff06f127ae878fe9d0d.jpg&h=f009a55c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那廢艦遼寧號<br />\n在烏克蘭建於80年代未 生銹20年後售到中國<br />\n實際使用不足五年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/110023_4d5cec52d02c979cc9b7c598b1d1482f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F110023_4d5cec52d02c979cc9b7c598b1d1482f.jpg&h=6a52e9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同場加影：<br />\n<br />\n美國1960年代服役的指揮艦<br />\n剛剛進船塢狀態<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/110400_f149a4c09ca4649515f161d534d5b66f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F110400_f149a4c09ca4649515f161d534d5b66f.jpg&h=9e720ba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">落得水就會生銹？<br />\n你當我三歲細路哥呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"7b8955b2f713f51829d4f9ebaf2646fc26f9f1c3","tid":312990,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375427a6e1e63f5b403ad29fdb36f7c9640e6ebc","tid":312990,"uid":16731,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017